      <title>由于拨备激增，Raiffeisen 九年来首次出现亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/raiffeisen-posts-first-loss-in-nine-years-as-provisions-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥匈帝国莱夫艾森银行国际股份公司 (Raiffeisen Bank International AG) 因被迫拨出 8.4 亿欧元来应对俄罗斯的不利法庭裁决，出现了九年来的首次季度净亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/raiffeisen-posts-first-loss-in-nine-years-as-provisions-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 08:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
