    <item>
      <title>瑞银计划回购 30 亿美元股票，等待瑞士资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/ubs-boosts-share-buyback-as-fourth-quarter-profit-beats-estimate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团表示，其计划今年回购最多 30 亿美元的自有股票，这表明其在等待对其资本水平的关键监管裁决时充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/ubs-boosts-share-buyback-as-fourth-quarter-profit-beats-estimate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:47:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京以谷歌调查回击特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-probes-google-moments-after-trump-s-tariffs-enter-effect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国针对唐纳德·特朗普发起的贸易战关税采取了报复措施，针对少数美国公司并对部分美国商品征收关税，此举似乎是为了避免世界两大经济体之间的紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-probes-google-moments-after-trump-s-tariffs-enter-effect</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对美国关税采取报复措施，股市持稳：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者猜测中国在报复性关税方面的克制可能有助于避免新兴贸易战出现最坏情况，美国股指期货企稳，美元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
